@node Music
The Music menu has only one item: ReDraw (Amiga-D).  Selecting this item
will re-draw the main display window, reflecting any changes in the form.

The reason that the screen is not re-drawn automatically after form
changes is to avoid stalling the music.  The only automatic redraw is
after a @{" Load Form  A-L " link "loadform"} operation.
@endnode

